{# Genre guidance #}
Genre: {{ style_guide.genre }}
{%- if style_guide.genre == 'fantasy' %} - Use rich, immersive descriptions. Include wonder and magic naturally.
{%- elif style_guide.genre == 'sci-fi' %} - Use precise, technical language. Make technology feel real and grounded.
{%- elif style_guide.genre == 'mystery' %} - Build suspense through careful revelation. Plant clues subtly.
{%- elif style_guide.genre == 'romance' %} - Focus on emotions and chemistry. Use sensory details.
{%- elif style_guide.genre == 'thriller' %} - Keep pace fast and tense. Use short, punchy sentences for action.
{%- elif style_guide.genre == 'horror' %} - Build dread through atmosphere. Use unsettling imagery.
{%- else %} - Tell an engaging story.
{%- endif %}

{# Tone guidance #}
Tone: {{ style_guide.tone }}
