{%- elif style_guide.tone == 'dark' %} - Use shadow and weight. Let moral ambiguity seep in.
{%- elif style_guide.tone == 'humorous' %} - Find natural moments of levity. Use wit over slapstick.
{%- elif style_guide.tone == 'epic' %} - Use grand, sweeping language. Make events feel momentous.
{%- elif style_guide.tone == 'intimate' %} - Focus on small, personal moments. Use close perspective.
{%- elif style_guide.tone == 'mysterious' %} - Leave questions unanswered. Build intrigue gradually.
{%- else %} - Maintain consistent mood.
{%- endif %}

